Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: "Gray Raven and Kamui... I'm relieved that all of you are fine.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Celica', 3: "We're currently sending another aircraft over to pick you up.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'The desert here is full of Corrupted, we need to keep moving to avoid being attacked.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Celica', 3: "Of course, I'll keep updating the pilots of your current location.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Celica', 3: "Oh right, the mission time was quite long this time, well done to all of you. I'll get the hot water running to welcome you back.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Thank you, Miss Celica... Hm? Hot water?', 4: '2'}
